sequenceDiagram
    actor Client as 客户端
    participant API as REST API
    participant DB as 数据库

    Client->>API: POST /api/auth/login<br/>{username, password}
    API->>DB: 查询用户
    DB-->>API: 用户信息
    API->>API: 校验密码
    API->>API: 生成 JWT Token
    API-->>Client: {code:200, data:{token, user}}

    Note over Client,API: 后续请求携带 Token

    Client->>API: GET /api/users/me<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}
    API->>API: 解析 Token, 提取 userId
    API->>DB: 查询用户
    DB-->>API: 用户信息
    API-->>Client: {code:200, data:{id, username, role}}
